---
import VantageLayout from '../../../layouts/VantageLayout.astro';
import { brand } from '../../../data/vantage';
---

<VantageLayout title="Medical Weight Loss — VANTAGE Men's Health" description="Structured medical weight management with labs, GLP-1 evaluation, body composition support, and provider oversight.">

<!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
<section class="vt-s vt-s--black mwl-hero">
	<div class="vt-w mwl-hero__layout">
		<div class="mwl-hero__copy">
			<span class="vt-e">Medical Weight Loss</span>
			<h1>Weight management guided by labs, not willpower alone.</h1>
			<p class="vt-sub">Stubborn weight gain — especially around the midsection — can be driven by hormonal, metabolic, or inflammatory factors. A proper evaluation can help identify what's working against you.</p>
			<div class="vt-btn-row">
				<a class="vt-btn vt-btn--red" href="/demos/hormone-trt/assessment">Take the Assessment &rarr;</a>
				<a class="vt-btn vt-btn--dark" href="/demos/hormone-trt/book-consultation">Book Consultation</a>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="mwl-hero__card" aria-hidden="true">
			<div class="mwl-hero__card-hdr">Contributing Factors</div>
			<div class="mwl-hero__card-row"><span class="mwl-hero__card-marker"></span><span>Hormonal imbalance</span></div>
			<div class="mwl-hero__card-row"><span class="mwl-hero__card-marker"></span><span>Insulin resistance</span></div>
			<div class="mwl-hero__card-row"><span class="mwl-hero__card-marker"></span><span>Chronic inflammation</span></div>
			<div class="mwl-hero__card-row"><span class="mwl-hero__card-marker"></span><span>Sleep &amp; stress dysregulation</span></div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ BEYOND WILLPOWER — numbered rows ═══ -->
<section class="vt-s vt-s--charcoal mwl-beyond">
	<div class="vt-w">
		<span class="vt-e">Beyond Willpower</span>
		<h2>Why diets fail when your biology is working against you</h2>
		<p class="vt-sub">Most men who struggle with weight have already tried calorie restriction and exercise. When results plateau or reverse, the issue is often metabolic — not motivational.</p>
		<p class="mwl-body">Low testosterone, insulin resistance, elevated cortisol, thyroid dysfunction, and poor sleep can all create a metabolic environment where fat storage is favored over fat loss. Medical weight management addresses these underlying factors.</p>
		<div class="mwl-beyond__factors">
			<div class="mwl-beyond__row">
				<span class="mwl-beyond__num">01</span>
				<span class="vt-redline"></span>
				<div class="mwl-beyond__content">
					<h3>Hormonal imbalance</h3>
					<p>Low testosterone promotes visceral fat storage and reduces lean muscle mass.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="mwl-beyond__row">
				<span class="mwl-beyond__num">02</span>
				<span class="vt-redline"></span>
				<div class="mwl-beyond__content">
					<h3>Insulin resistance</h3>
					<p>Elevated insulin levels can make it nearly impossible to mobilize stored body fat.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="mwl-beyond__row">
				<span class="mwl-beyond__num">03</span>
				<span class="vt-redline"></span>
				<div class="mwl-beyond__content">
					<h3>Inflammation</h3>
					<p>Chronic low-grade inflammation can disrupt hunger signaling and metabolic function.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="mwl-beyond__row">
				<span class="mwl-beyond__num">04</span>
				<span class="vt-redline"></span>
				<div class="mwl-beyond__content">
					<h3>Sleep & stress</h3>
					<p>Cortisol dysregulation and poor sleep compound metabolic dysfunction.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ YOUR PATHWAY — horizontal connected steps ═══ -->
<section class="vt-s vt-s--carbon mwl-pathway">
	<div class="vt-w">
		<span class="vt-e">Your Pathway</span>
		<h2>A structured approach to medical weight management</h2>
		<div class="mwl-pathway__track">
			<div class="mwl-pathway__step mwl-pathway__step--active">
				<div class="mwl-pathway__dot"></div>
				<span class="mwl-pathway__num">Step 01</span>
				<span class="mwl-pathway__label">Comprehensive metabolic assessment</span>
				<p class="mwl-pathway__desc">Labs including fasting insulin, HbA1c, thyroid, hormones, and inflammatory markers to map your metabolic baseline.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="mwl-pathway__step">
				<div class="mwl-pathway__dot"></div>
				<span class="mwl-pathway__num">Step 02</span>
				<span class="mwl-pathway__label">Provider consultation</span>
				<p class="mwl-pathway__desc">Review results, identify metabolic roadblocks, and discuss treatment options — including GLP-1 eligibility.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="mwl-pathway__step">
				<div class="mwl-pathway__dot"></div>
				<span class="mwl-pathway__num">Step 03</span>
				<span class="mwl-pathway__label">Personalized protocol</span>
				<p class="mwl-pathway__desc">A treatment plan addressing your specific metabolic factors — may include medication, hormone optimization, or both.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="mwl-pathway__step">
				<div class="mwl-pathway__dot"></div>
				<span class="mwl-pathway__num">Step 04</span>
				<span class="mwl-pathway__label">Regular monitoring & adjustment</span>
				<p class="mwl-pathway__desc">Ongoing lab checks, body composition tracking, and protocol refinements to sustain progress.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ GLP-1 MEDICATIONS — split with bordered panels ═══ -->
<section class="vt-s vt-s--charcoal mwl-glp1">
	<div class="vt-w">
		<span class="vt-e">GLP-1 Medications</span>
		<h2>GLP-1 receptor agonists: evaluation & oversight</h2>
		<p class="mwl-body">GLP-1 medications (such as semaglutide and tirzepatide) may be appropriate for men who meet specific clinical criteria. At VANTAGE, eligibility is determined through labs and provider evaluation — not self-selection.</p>
		<p class="mwl-body" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">These medications can support significant weight reduction when combined with metabolic optimization and provider oversight. They are not prescribed without proper evaluation, and ongoing monitoring is required.</p>
		<div class="mwl-glp1__panels">
			<div class="mwl-glp1__panel">
				<div class="mwl-glp1__panel-hdr"><span>Candidacy</span><span>Evaluation Required</span></div>
				<div class="mwl-glp1__panel-body">
					<h3>Who may be a candidate</h3>
					<ul class="mwl-list">
						<li><span class="mwl-list__marker"></span>BMI ≥ 30, or ≥ 27 with metabolic comorbidities</li>
						<li><span class="mwl-list__marker"></span>Prior failed attempts with diet and exercise alone</li>
						<li><span class="mwl-list__marker"></span>Lab-confirmed metabolic dysfunction</li>
						<li><span class="mwl-list__marker"></span>No contraindications identified on evaluation</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="mwl-glp1__panel">
				<div class="mwl-glp1__panel-hdr"><span>Oversight</span><span>Ongoing</span></div>
				<div class="mwl-glp1__panel-body">
					<h3>What's included in oversight</h3>
					<ul class="mwl-list">
						<li><span class="mwl-list__marker"></span>Dose titration guided by response and tolerability</li>
						<li><span class="mwl-list__marker"></span>Regular lab monitoring (metabolic + hormonal panels)</li>
						<li><span class="mwl-list__marker"></span>Provider check-ins at each dose adjustment</li>
						<li><span class="mwl-list__marker"></span>Lean mass preservation strategies</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ FINAL CTA — red background panel ═══ -->
<section class="mwl-final">
	<div class="vt-w mwl-final__inner">
		<span class="vt-e">Get Started</span>
		<h2>Ready to understand what's driving your weight?</h2>
		<p class="vt-sub">A metabolic evaluation can reveal factors that willpower alone cannot overcome. Start with an assessment.</p>
		<div class="vt-btn-row" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
			<a class="vt-btn vt-btn--red" href="/demos/hormone-trt/assessment">Take the Assessment &rarr;</a>
			<a class="vt-btn vt-btn--dark" href="/demos/hormone-trt/book-consultation">Book Consultation</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ DISCLAIMER ═══ -->
<div class="vt-s--black" style="padding:0 0 2rem;">
	<div class="vt-w">
		<p class="mwl-disc">{brand.disclaimer}</p>
	</div>
</div>

</VantageLayout>

<style>
/* ═══ HERO — dark compact with contributing factors card ═══ */
.mwl-hero { padding: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 8rem) 0 clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.mwl-hero__layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr; gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4rem); align-items: center; }
.mwl-hero__copy h1 { max-width: 700px; }
.mwl-hero__copy .vt-sub { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.mwl-hero__card { background: var(--vt-charcoal); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border-radius: var(--vt-r); overflow: hidden; border-top: 3px solid var(--vt-red); }
.mwl-hero__card-hdr { padding: 0.75rem 1rem; font-size: 0.58rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--vt-white); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
.mwl-hero__card-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem; padding: 0.7rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(244,239,231,0.55); font-weight: 600; }
.mwl-hero__card-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.mwl-hero__card-marker { flex-shrink: 0; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--vt-red); }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .mwl-hero__layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .mwl-hero__card { max-width: 360px; } }

/* ═══ BEYOND WILLPOWER — numbered rows ═══ */
.mwl-beyond h2 { max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.mwl-beyond .vt-sub { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.mwl-body { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(244,239,231,0.5); line-height: 1.55; max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.mwl-beyond__factors { margin-top: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.mwl-beyond__row { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.25rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--vt-border); }
.mwl-beyond__row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.mwl-beyond__num { flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--vt-red); padding-top: 0.15rem; min-width: 1.8rem; }
.mwl-beyond__row .vt-redline { margin-top: 0.55rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
.mwl-beyond__content h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
.mwl-beyond__content p { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(244,239,231,0.5); line-height: 1.55; }

/* ═══ PATHWAY — horizontal connected-step track ═══ */
.mwl-pathway h2 { max-width: 520px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
.mwl-pathway__track { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-radius: var(--vt-r); overflow: hidden; }
.mwl-pathway__step { padding: 1.25rem 1rem; background: var(--vt-charcoal); position: relative; }
.mwl-pathway__dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.mwl-pathway__step--active .mwl-pathway__dot { background: var(--vt-red); border-color: var(--vt-red); box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(215,25,32,0.3); }
.mwl-pathway__num { display: block; font-size: 0.55rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--vt-red); margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
.mwl-pathway__label { display: block; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--vt-bone); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
.mwl-pathway__desc { font-size: 0.68rem; color: rgba(244,239,231,0.45); line-height: 1.45; }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .mwl-pathway__track { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

/* ═══ GLP-1 — side-by-side bordered panels ═══ */
.mwl-glp1 h2 { max-width: 520px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.mwl-glp1__panels { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-radius: var(--vt-r); overflow: hidden; }
.mwl-glp1__panel { background: var(--vt-carbon); display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.mwl-glp1__panel-hdr { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 0.65rem 1.25rem; font-size: 0.55rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--vt-white); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
.mwl-glp1__panel-hdr span:last-child { color: var(--vt-steel); font-weight: 600; }
.mwl-glp1__panel-body { padding: 1.25rem; flex: 1; }
.mwl-glp1__panel-body h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.mwl-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
.mwl-list li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.55rem; font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(244,239,231,0.5); line-height: 1.55; }
.mwl-list__marker { flex-shrink: 0; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--vt-red); }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .mwl-glp1__panels { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

/* ═══ FINAL CTA — red background panel ═══ */
.mwl-final { background: var(--vt-red); padding: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem) 0; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.mwl-final::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -30%; right: -5%; width: 40%; height: 160%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.08); transform: skewX(-12deg); pointer-events: none; }
.mwl-final__inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 560px; }
.mwl-final h2 { color: var(--vt-white); }
.mwl-final .vt-e { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
.mwl-final .vt-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
.mwl-final .vt-btn--red { background: var(--vt-white); color: var(--vt-red); border-color: var(--vt-white); }
.mwl-final .vt-btn--red:hover { background: var(--vt-bone); }
.mwl-final .vt-btn--dark { background: transparent; color: var(--vt-white); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }
.mwl-final .vt-btn--dark:hover { border-color: var(--vt-white); }

/* ═══ DISCLAIMER ═══ */
.mwl-disc { font-size: 0.55rem; color: rgba(244,239,231,0.12); font-style: italic; max-width: 560px; }
</style>
